<Group view="code" labelreference="L485" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">#mx2 gets the squared difference between the average predicted and actual migrations. This difference is then minimized to get a beta (c) for each nu (a) that gives the correct predicted migration:</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group view="code" labelreference="L454" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">mx2:=proc(a,c) options notrace; global tbad,ik,badarray,badstot,enda,PredRes,PredLambda;
p:=0; tbad:=0;

for k from 1 to castes do;
stk:=(k-1)*N+1;
enk:=stk+N-1;

sa:=mxj(a,c,stk,enk);
#showx7(sa);


#Fill PredRes matrix with predicted migrations:
for i from 1 to N do;
PredRes[stk+i-1,1]:=op(i,sa[1]);
end do;

#Fill PredLambda matrix with predicted lambdas:
for i from 1 to (N-1) do;
PredLambda[stk+i-1,1]:=op(2,op(i,op(2,sa[2]))):
end do;



tbad:=tbad+sa[3];
badarray[k]:=sa[4];

for i from 1 to N do;
badstot[N*(k-1)+i]:=sa[3];
end do;

end do;

# Finish PredLambda matrix by getting the difference:
for i from 1 to tot do:
PredLambda[i,3]:= (PredLambda[i,2]-PredLambda[i,1]);
end do: 

#Get average predicted migration:
avgpred:=add(PredRes[i,1],i=1..tot)/tot;

#squared error for average predicted migration:
p:=(avgpred-averagemig)^2;

ik:=ik+1;

if trunc(ik/20)=ik/20 then 
 show(p,a,c);
end if;
p;
end proc;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Output>
<Text-field style="HyperlinkWarning" layout="HyperlinkWarning"><Hyperlink linktarget="http://www.maplesoft.com/support/help/errors/view.aspx?path=Warning,%20%60p%60%20is%20implicitly%20declared%20local%20to%20procedure%20%60mx2%60" hyperlink="true"><Font style="HyperlinkWarning">Warning, `p` is implicitly declared local to procedure `mx2`</Font></Hyperlink></Text-field>
</Output>
<Output>
<Text-field style="HyperlinkWarning" layout="HyperlinkWarning"><Hyperlink linktarget="http://www.maplesoft.com/support/help/errors/view.aspx?path=Warning,%20%60k%60%20is%20implicitly%20declared%20local%20to%20procedure%20%60mx2%60" hyperlink="true"><Font style="HyperlinkWarning">Warning, `k` is implicitly declared local to procedure `mx2`</Font></Hyperlink></Text-field>
</Output>
<Output>
<Text-field style="HyperlinkWarning" layout="HyperlinkWarning"><Hyperlink linktarget="http://www.maplesoft.com/support/help/errors/view.aspx?path=Warning,%20%60stk%60%20is%20implicitly%20declared%20local%20to%20procedure%20%60mx2%60" hyperlink="true"><Font style="HyperlinkWarning">Warning, `stk` is implicitly declared local to procedure `mx2`</Font></Hyperlink></Text-field>
